<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.294239>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 10. Aleutihenricia federi, Holotype, USNM 1125115. Fig. 5, Ray, abactinal view. Bar = 5.0 cm. Fig. 6, Ray, actinal view. Bar = 5.0 cm. Fig. 7, Close-up, abactinal surface. Bar = 2.0 mm. Fig. 8, Close-up of actino-lateral surface of ray, near the base of the ray, illustrating arrangement of skeletal ossicles. (AD) adambulacrals; (VL) ventral laterals. Bar = 3.0 mm Fig. 9, Close-up of adambulacral region of ray. Bar = 2.0 cm. Fig. 10, Close-up of oral region. Bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/294239/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

